INSERT Items(ID,Titel,Categorie,Postcode,Locatie,Land,Verkoper,Prijs,Valuta,Conditie,Thumbnail,Beschrijving) VALUES (331388038020,'Recon Snow2 HUD Head-up display with Uvex G.GL9 goggle en 2 remotes',13394,'2584GM','Nederland','NL','tieluh1','315.0','EUR','Nieuw: Overige (zie details)','img331388038020.jpg','<h2 style="margin: 0px 0px 0.7em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); line-height: 1; font-family: sans-serif;">Product Description</h2><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">Snow2 is our fourth generation Heads-up Display (HUD) for alpine sports. Snow2 is considerably more powerful, more efficient, and more amazing than any device we have ever built. It is truly our most advanced HUD yet.</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">Snow2 comes packed with an incredibly powerful and efficient dual-core processor resulting in 3x the processing power and a 35% increase in battery life from previous generation HUDs. Snow2 now has a dedicated graphics processing unit providing much better brightness and contrast, greatly increasing screen readability. Blur on the screen’s edges is virtually non-existent with Snow2′s WQVGA widescreen display. Finally, Snow2 adds much improved connectivity options with&nbsp;Wi-Fi (IEEE802.11a/b/g/n) and Made for iPhone certification resulting in a greatly enhanced iPhone pairing and connection experience.</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">Snow2 comes with the following features out of the box:</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Performance Stats</strong><br>Snow2 delivers crisp graphics and vital information when you want them, and keeps them out-of-sight when you don’t. Everything from speed, vertical descent, jump airtime, navigation and distance are calculated and displayed using a built-in precision GPS and an integrated suite of sensors. In other words, you’ll always know just how fast you’re going, how many jumps you took, and how much ground you’re covering.</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Navigation &amp; Buddy Tracking</strong><br>The built-in GPS enables full resort navigation, and when paired with a compatible Android or iOS device, you’ll have real-time buddy tracking delivered direct-to-eye. The days of soggy paper trail maps are over – always know where you’ve been, where you’re going, and where your friends are.</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Smartphone Connectivity</strong><br>In addition to buddy tracking, pairing with a compatible Android or iOS smartphone will allow you to receive texts and call display, and access your music player controls all from within the HUD. Keep your expensive smartphone safe in your pocket while still staying connected.</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Trip Viewing &amp; Sharing</strong><br>Things happen fast on the mountain, and your HUD tracks it all. With the Engage website and mobile apps, you are able to download and process all the data that your HUD has recorded. From this platform you can review your stats and achievements, and share these experiences online via your social media accounts.</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Key Features</strong><br>· Speed<br>· Jump Analytics<br>· Vertical<br>· Distance<br>· Altitude<br>· Navigation<br>· Buddy Tracking<br>· Call Display<br>· Incoming SMS Texts &amp; Canned SMS responses<br>· Music Player Control</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;">Goggle: UVEX G.GL 9</strong><br>The fighter-pilot styled, reflective, over-sized lens facilitates a great range of visibility. In powder, the frameless exterior construction means even the heaviest of sprays glides off the goggle without sticking to the frame or affecting your sight. Whether worn over or under the helmet, the extra wide goggle strap always keeps the goggle in place.</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px;">2 remotes so 1 spare</p><br>')
